  "title": "重复",
  "content": "<p data-pid=\"00qfzw9P\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Spaced_repetition\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">间隔重复</a><sup data-text=\"间隔重复（spaced repetition）\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/305651556\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup>中的<b>重复</b>或<b>回顾</b>代表从记忆中提取信息的行为。在 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/SuperMemo\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">SuperMemo</a><sup data-text=\"什么是 SuperMemo\" data-url=\"https://www.yuque.com/supermemo/wiki/supermemo\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"2\">[2]</sup> 中，它通常遵循以下步骤：</p><ol><li data-pid=\"ehsN5Rtz\"> 学习者被问及一个问题<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"pqM6dGnS\"> 学习者回答该问题（比如，在心里默念）<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"L_6epZ4E\"> 学习者为回答的准确性<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Grade\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">评分</a><br/> </li></ol><p data-pid=\"5xEr7Ma5\">术语<b>回顾</b>还可以指在<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Incremental_reading\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">渐进阅读</a><sup data-text=\"渐进阅读\" data-url=\"https://www.yuque.com/supermemo/wiki/incremental_reading\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"3\">[3]</sup>中对文本片段进行被动阅读的行为。</p><p data-pid=\"MMhFIJDj\">参见：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//help.supermemo.org/wiki/Learn\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">SuperMemo 中的重复循环</a></p><blockquote data-pid=\"emsWx25g\">本<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Glossary\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">词汇表</a>条目用于解释 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/SuperMemo_Guru\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">SuperMemo</a>，一位自 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/History_of_spaced_repetition_%28print%29\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">1987</a><sup data-text=\"《间隔重复的历史》\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/375379522\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"4\">[4]</sup> 年以来的<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Spaced_repetition\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">间隔重复</a>软件先驱。</blockquote><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><blockquote data-pid=\"SzqU43Iu\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a> 汉化组译制<br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Repetition\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Repetition - supermemo.guru</a></blockquote>",
